clause.p:
Load cells that are equipped with functions typically performed by complete instruments may be required to be evaluated against additional requirements contained in other OIML Recommendations for those complete instruments. These additional evaluations are outside the scope of this Recommendation (see  2.3
 and Figure 2
).
